rows.label: qst101106_msg0001
rows.name:
Ah! That must have been
heavy! Thank you.

rows.label: qst101106_msg0002
rows.name:
With this, I can make the best
furniture by the deadline.

rows.label: qst101106_msg0003
rows.name:
I have a lot to say about that
Superbian official, but...

rows.label: qst101106_msg0004
rows.name:
that's no reason to do a half-hearted
job. It would ruin my reputation
as a furniture craftsman.

rows.label: qst101106_msg0005
rows.name:
Everyone who makes things in
Torigo thinks the same way.

rows.label: qst101106_msg0007
rows.name:
I don't know what would have happened
if you hadn't spoken to me...

rows.label: qst101106_msg0008
rows.name:
If you finish your journey and
decide to settle down, please
let me make your furniture.
